<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">
Erratum:<P>Unfortunately, the equations worked out earlier for the distance between Luclin and Norrath were not only wrong, but they were more congenial than the correct formulae. In reality, the distance (d) to Norrath from Luclin appears to satisfy tan(70.8/2)=18/(18+d), or d=18/tan(35.4)-18=7.3 miles; the distance (d) to Luclin from Norrath should solve tan(5.3/2)=1.3/(1.3+d), or d=1.3/tan(2.65)-1.3=26.8 miles. But the distance from the surface of one to the surface of the other should always be the same, and 26.8 does not equal 7.3. Someone at Verant clearly did not do their homework, or maybe I am just being too crude in my work. We can hope further developments in the games will lead to new perspectives literally becoming available, and the solution to our problem.<P>[ 04-30-2002: Message edited by: Reshokor Muiren ]<p>[ 04-30-2002: Message edited by: Reshokor Muiren ]
</FONT>
